Sahlen and Associates Incsaid it has completed the purchase of Gleason SecuritiesService Inc of New York and Gleason Plant Security Inc ofConnecticut.    Sahlen said the deal's terms were not disclosed, but addedthat the acquired companies had combined annual revenues ofover 18 mln dlrs.    Sahlen, a private invetigation company, said the Gleasoncompanies provide security guard services to corporations inthe tri-state area.    Reuter&#3;